"{\"uid\": \"marinelink.com-news-ulstein-verft-begins-outfitting-olympics-513562\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"May 8, 2024 (Photo: Ulstein) The second in a series of new construction service operation vessels (CSOV) being built for Olympic has entered the outfitting phase.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 3}, {\"ngram\": \"(Photo\", \"from\": 12, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \": Ulstein\", \"from\": 18, \"to\": 27}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 43, \"to\": 51}, {\"ngram\": \"new construction service operation vessels\", \"from\": 55, \"to\": 97}, {\"ngram\": \"CSOV\", \"from\": 99, \"to\": 103}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 128}, {\"ngram\": \"the outfitting phase\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The newbuild was towed from the Crist hull yard in Poland, arriving on Wednesday at Ulstein Verft in Norway where the outfitting phase will now begin.\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 217, \"end\": 223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9914276479437863, \"rank\": 0.005344179151871742, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}, {\"begin\": 267, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999290594, \"rank\": 7.102717338995658e-11, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The newbuild\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 178}, {\"ngram\": \"the Crist hull yard\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"Ulstein Verft\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"the outfitting phase\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vessel was towed into the dock hall where the paint work will be performed.\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vessel\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"the dock hall\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"the paint work\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Commissioning and testing will take place in the project's concluding months.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"the project's concluding months\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022, Olympic and Ulstein signed a contract on ship design and construction of two CSOVs of the ULSTEIN SX222 design from Ulstein Design & Solutions AS.\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein\", \"score\": 0.9998651631990366, \"rank\": 0.0001348549842531098, \"text\": \"Ulstein\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 492}, {\"ngram\": \"a contract\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"ship design\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"construction\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"two CSOVs\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 567}, {\"ngram\": \"the ULSTEIN SX222 design\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"Ulstein Design\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"Solutions\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hulls are constructed by Crist, while Ulstein Verft is the overall responsible for the construction project, including electrical and mechanical installations, piping, accommodation and system integration.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, 